title: Zillow Profit View Misses on Cool Housing Market, Legal Costs
description: Zillow Group Inc. forecast first-quarter profit that falls short of analyst estimates as the home-search site balances legal costs from ongoing litigation and expenses from the company’s partnership with Redfin.
